outfit_data.top: A cream silk blouse with exaggerated puff sleeves, featuring a dramatic high neckline and an asymmetric drape that falls to the hip.
outfit_data.bottom: Camel wool wide-leg trousers with a sharp crease down the center, cinched at the waist with a statement belt in taupe leather. The pants have a flowing silhouette, pooling slightly at the ankles for a modern touch.
outfit_data.shoes: Black suede stiletto heels, reaching mid-calf, with pointed toes and a subtly buckled strap around the ankle.
outfit_data.extras: A chunky gold chain necklace layered with delicate silver pendants.
